attributionInfo.agentName: Jennie & Eddie Luxury Living Boston Team

description: Authentic Brick and Beam Loft for sale in Boston’s ultra-hip Fort Point neighborhood; uniquely positioned at the crossroads between the Waterfront District and the ever-expanding Seaport. Boasting 13ft ceilings & 7 south-facing windows, this luxurious Loft offers a most thoughtfully designed layout, with a modern kitchen with Bosch appliances, honed black granite counters & Zebrawood cabinetry, a deep walk-in with California Closet built-ins, a laundry closet with stacked W/D conveniently within the luxe bathroom, a high efficiency HVAC system, plus a private office retreat (13ft deep x 9ft wide) that easily doubles as a proper guest bedroom! When walking into the building’s chic welcoming lounge, you’ll be met by its vintage character and its modern amenities of package room and elevator with direct access to a common roof-deck with superb skyline city-views, a secure bike storage room and private storage cages in basement, plus on-site dining by local favorite 'Citrus & Salt' bistro.
